channel.title: Sounds Under Radio - Waking Up The Satellites (Full, free download)
channel.description:
I recently heard this song at the end of a movie I was watching, I liked it so I tried finding the name of the song on the internet. I found it on youtube, I wanted to try download it but I couldn't find it anywhere. I contacted the artists and they sent me a copy of the song, they also said I could post the song. So why not? :)
Proof:
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/dpcxfk.jpg[/img]
Download:
- http://www.mediafire.com/?ymdix5ndzjy
Or listen to it here:
- http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wNL44vpAJIU
~Jayden.
